This directory contains various distribution configuration files,
patches, and start scripts:

* bucardo.rc

Sample BSD rc file for controlling Bucardo.

* bucardo.spec

RPM spec file for RHEL 7/8 and Fedora.

* bucardo.service

systemd unit file for using with systemctl, used by the RPM.

* bucardorc

Sample /etc/bucardorc file installed by the RPM.

* bucardo-logfiles.patch

Patch to set the default directory for log files to /var/log/bucardo, used by the RPM.

* bucardo.init

Sample SysV chkconfig-style start script for controlling Bucardo on non-systemd Linux distributions.
